Title: More Doors To Open
Description:
There are still more vaults, but there aren't enough of us to explore them all.

That's where you come in. Could you look for more keys? Then we can continue exploring the vaults.

Tacha and I will stay here and work on documenting our earlier discoveries. That's tough work, but one of us has to do it. Okay, two of us. But it is a lot of work, I assure you.
ObjectivesText: Enter and explore additional Zskera Vaults.

Objectives.Text: Speak with PathfinderJeb to enter the vault
Doors opened with Zskera Vault Keys
